{"tid":1786683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遊說全世界倒數完一齊用粵語喊八個字","createTime":"2019-12-17T10:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T16:27:26.000Z","uid":6845,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4032e28287670a1c09753722d4076943887b5b","tid":1786683,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命<br />\n<br />\n要畫面有畫面，又比到野外國人一齊做，成本低，又希望可以帶返起粵語一直受盡打壓呢件事<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">根據民間組織「港語學」統計，現時約有七成小學，以及四成中學推行普教中。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭語同台語就係例子，無左語言，好多相關嘅文化都會失去 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">要消滅一個民族，首先瓦解它的文化；要瓦解它的文化，首先消滅承載它的語言；要消滅這種語言，首先先從他們的學校裡下手。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n點解唔倒數8秒係因為隔離post話無氣勢，而且可以要你2揀1喊口號定happynewyear重要啲。"},{"pid":"a522bede5e7b63aa6bf915bc488931421c6f34c6","tid":1786683,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"24號記得出黎"},{"pid":"b4cdaccfd12c162d67745cb9d7ccc9cf5ffed1da","tid":1786683,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 <br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默🈲❌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784354</a>"},{"pid":"eb835c2102d833f7b8c2677bde66206095eabbbe","tid":1786683,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:12:18.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰線外國戰線又有野可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83610ece13056a0801d19601b2b5c14cc5886433","tid":1786683,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aba0cfa48bc2fb263c89632cf19e23a04d26b8","tid":1786683,"uid":272424,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"太on9了<br />\n我會叫返happy new year"},{"pid":"d8c2dc17f84b74ce2a8bbbdb6891c97b43414645","tid":1786683,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":